container class -> superclass -> subclass
note            -> source     -> film_source

Superclass methods
------------------
source              # Superclass instance
source.title        # Superclass attribute
source.duration     # Subclass attribute
source.film_source  # Subclass instance
source.film_source= # Subclass assignment
source.film
source.film=
Source.create_film_source
Source.build_film_source
Source.container_classes
source.subclass
source.subclass_instance

Subclass methods
----------------
film_source.superclass
film_source.superclass_instance
film_source.source
FilmSource.create
film_source.save
film_source.destroy

Container class methods
-----------------------
note.source
note.film_source
note.source = Source.new || FilmSource.new
note.film_source = Source.new || FilmSource.new

To create a subclass:
---------------------
FilmSource.create(superclass_instance: source)
source.create_film_source
note.create_film_source